---
import Plants from "../../svgs/Plants.astro";
import Rectangle from "../../svgs/Rectangle.astro";
import Waves from "../../svgs/Waves.astro";
import Whatsapp from "../../svgs/Whatsapp.astro";
---

<section id="about-section" class="relative flex flex-col justify-center items-center lg:flex-row mt-10 mb-20 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center text-secondary-500 lg:hidden uppercase tracking-wide">Sobre Mí</h2>
    <div class="max-w-[504px] mx-4 basis-2/4 relative">
      <div class="relative z-50">
        <img
            src="./about-image.webp"
            loading="lazy"
            alt="Retrato de Felipe Pollitzer en la seccion sobre mi"
            class="mt-10 rounded-xl about-me-shadow"
            width="504"
            height="465"
        />
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[#FF885B] opacity-10 rounded-xl"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 text-lg mx-4 sm:max-w-[504px] lg:mt-10 basis-2/4">
      <h2 class="hidden font-black text-5xl text-left text-secondary-500 lg:block uppercase tracking-wide">Sobre Mí</h2>
      <p class="lg:mt-8 text-[#33372C]">
        ¡Hola! Soy Felipe Pollitzer, coach ontológico con ganas de acompañarte en
        tu camino de transformación personal y profesional. Mi enfoque se basa en
        la creencia de que todos tenemos el potencial de vivir una vida auténtica
        y plena, y mi misión es ayudarte a descubrir y desbloquear ese potencial.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-[#33372C]">
        Quiero ayudarte a identificar y superar los obstáculos internos que te
        impiden avanzar. No se trata solo de alcanzar metas, sino de redefinir la
        manera en que te relacionas contigo mismo y con el mundo.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 md:self-start">
        <a class="flex w-full md:w-auto " href="#contact-section">
        <button
          class="bg-secondary-500 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity text-white w-full py-2 rounded-lg mt-8 text-xl md:w-[180px] lg:mt-12 lg:w-[217px] lg:text-xl xl:mt-10"
          >Hablemos</button
        >
      </a>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://wa.me/541133961603" class="hidden border md:flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-1 mt-8 rounded-md lg:mt-12 xl:mt-10 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors cursor-pointer"><Whatsapp stroke="#2c3e50" class="w-[36px] h-[36px]" /></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <Plants class="hidden lg:block absolute -bottom-52 w-[250px] left-0 xl:w-[321px] z-50" />
    <Rectangle class="hidden md:block absolute opacity-10 left-6 -top-20 md:-top-32 lg:-top-40 w-[180px] z-0" fill="#FF885B" />
    <Waves class="hidden md:block absolute w-[180px] right-6 md:-top-28 lg:-top-24 lg:w-[220px] z-0" />
    <Rectangle class="hidden md:block absolute opacity-10 right-6 md:-bottom-60 lg:-bottom-60 w-[180px] z-0" fill="#FF885B" />
    <Rectangle class="hidden md:block absolute opacity-10 right-36 md:-bottom-80 lg:-bottom-92 w-[120px] z-0" fill="#FF885B" />
  </section>


  <style>
    .about-me-shadow {
        filter: drop-shadow(0px 0px 10px #557C56);
      
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .about-me-shadow {
        filter: drop-shadow(-30px 30px #FF885B);
      }
    }
  </style>
  